# Plans Storage

All plans (implementation plans, architecture plans, feature plans, etc.) must be saved as markdown files in `development/plans/`.

- Use descriptive filenames with date prefix, e.g. `2026-05-26-initial-architecture.md`
- Do not store plans elsewhere in the repo

## After Plan Mode execution

When a plan is confirmed and executed, copy the final plan file into `development/plans/` with a date-prefixed descriptive filename. This ensures the development folder always contains the full history of decisions and executed plans, even though `development/` is git-ignored and plans in `.cursor/plans/` may be transient.
